Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveA few hours ago former media aide to ex-President Goodluck Ebele Jonathan Reno Omokri took to his verified Instagram page to react after a fan ask to see his wife’s real face without a sunscreen.


In his Instagram post, he uploaded a photo of himself and his beautiful wife and the lady with the social media name Joy Peters Onogwu who seems curious noted that she must be Ebele’s mother. Furthermore, she stated that she has been longing to know her for years now as she went on to ask that she would love to see her real face next time without her wearing a sunshade.
Mr. Reno Omokri who didn’t seem offended about the lady’s comment ask what does she mean by sunscreen. He, however, went on to reveal some intimate stuff about his woman as he affirms that everything one can see about the mother of his adorable children is natural as noting that he found her at home and asked her hand in marriage. In conclusion, he politely said to the young lady that she should go and inquire from the elders in her hometown to tell her the meaning of when a man marries a woman she saw at home



